/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf58.webp?t=1607637436\" width=54 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397620/extras/281b79f6d9d5bf3cae7709a4294cdf